Description: Ticket to a lecture by Professor Nogo on mummies, moonshine and steam at the Polyboisflois Institution, with a mummy at top pulled by a teapot, two lamps at the sides and the motto 'Scentia non sensualitas' at bottom; proof. Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Isaac Robert Cruikshank (?)
Curator's comments: The attribution was given for styilistic reasons. For a duplicate see 1868,0808.13051.
